Version        2.2    Woody

Boot            +       +
Network         +       +?
Shares          +       +
Time            +       +
Users           +       +?
Display         +       +
Internetsharing +       +
Font            ?       ?

Woody comments: You'll have to echo 'woody' > /etc/debian_version to
make the ximian-setup-tools detect your distribution. 


Linux Mandrake:

